<HEADLINE>
<P>
TONY SERRA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
If we ever needed reaffirmation of the need for a speedy trial and speedier 
application of the death penalty in capital cases, we have an outstanding 
example in Croy vs. the People. I would venture a guess that the family of 
Officer Hittson, myself and many others don't think J. Tony Serra is very 
"cute." 
</P>
<P>
WALTER MCWILLIAMS 
</P>
<P>
Newhall 
</P>
