<P>
AND FINALLY: Our Band Name of the Week (baseball division) goes to the New 
York-based group Honus Wagner (named after the great Pittsburgh Pirates 
shortstop), who are in town Monday at Al's Bar. . . . And if you're if looking 
for rap on the razor's edge, get a copy of "HollyWord," the new spoken-word 
