<P>
Cruises: Holland America offers about 70 Alaska cruises during the 
May-to-September season. 
</P>
<P>
The Westerdam, Rotterdam, Nieuw Amsterdam and Noordam are the backbone of the 
fleet. Prices per week start at about $1,000 per person, double occupancy. Get 
booking information from travel agents or Holland America Line, 300 Elliott 
Ave. W., Seattle, Wash. 98119, (800) 426-0327. 
</P>
<P>
Alaska Sightseeing Tours runs the Sheltered Seas on a May-to-September, three- 
and five-day cruise schedule. The yacht can carry about 100 passengers. 
</P>
