<DOCNO> LA081290-0169 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 260881 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 12, 1990, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 3; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
