Palos Verdes Tae Kwon Do Training Center. ; Photo, Chao, with Kwon Sung Choi, 
discusses strategy during a break in training. Choi was recently appointed 
coach of the U.S. National Team. ED COMPEAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 'She's 
a natural -- a genius of this martial art. The best I've ever seen. . . . 
Usually it takes three years to get a black belt. She took only two years, one 
month.' -- KWON SUNG CHOI Tae Kwon Do master 
</P>
