Hitler in "God's Country." CHRISTOPHER BRISCOE; Photo, Alan Berg United Press 
International; Photo, Robert Jay Mathews Associated Press; Photo, Tom Ramirez, 
left, plays murdered Denver talk-show host Alan Berg. ; Photo, Remi Sandri, 
left, portrays The Order's founder, Robert Jay Mathews. 
</P>
