led the way by rushing for 112 yards. DON KELSON / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
(Southland Edition) The Rams' George Bethune (57) has Chief quarterback Mike 
Elkins in his grasp, but the ball is elsewhere. DON KELSEN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA081290-0182 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 260912 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 12, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
