<P>
CROSSROADS COMPLETES PHASE IN MURRIETA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Crossroads Development has completed the first phase of its $75-million 
Murrieta Town Center in Murrieta Hot Springs. 
</P>
<P>
The 500,000-square-foot shopping center project is financed by Citicorp and is 
located on 44 acres at the juncture of Interstates 215, 15 and Murrieta Hot 
Springs Road. 
</P>
<P>
Construction on Phase 1 -- now fully leased -- began in July 1989. Phase 2 -- 
which is 70% preleased -- began last April and completion is scheduled for next 
January. 
</P>
