<P>
Copper Crest at Southridge, a 113-unit single-family development by Century 
Homes Communities, opens today in the SouthRidge planned community in Fontana. 
</P>
<P>
The first phase of 26 two-, three- and four-bedroom houses is priced from 
$120,990 to $157,990. The houses range in size from 897 to 1,770 square feet 
and have 2 or 2 1/2 baths. October move-ins are planned. There are parks and 
other recreational facilities in Southridge. 
</P>
<P>
Two furnished models are open from 9 a.m. to 6 p.m. daily at 15475 Old Castle 
Road, reached from the northbound Country Village Road exit of the Pomona (60) 
Freeway. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
