Showcase Custom Series at Southridge opens today in the Southridge planned 
community in Fontana, with 253 three-, four- and five-bedroom single-family 
houses. 
</P>
<P>
The 22 units in the first phase range in size from 1,710 to 2,454 square feet 
and are priced from $159,900 to $198,900. The builder is Showcase Homes. First 
move-ins are planned for December. 
