<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The map accompanying "On the Beach," June 24, indicated that Imperial Beach has 
been under quarantine since 1980. Actually, only the beach area adjacent to the 
Imperial Beach estuary and two miles northward is limited to sunbathing. The 
ocean off the city of Imperial Beach is tested frequently and is safe for 
swimming. 
</P>
