<P>
REAL LIFE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I just wanted to say how I enjoy all the "true life" informative programs now 
on TV -- most of all "Rescue 911" -- and the rest, i.e., "Cops," "Unsolved 
Mysteries," "PrimeTime Live," "48 Hours," "America's Most Wanted," "20/20." 
</P>
